	Defines sound, such as music or other audio streams.


	
		If present, the audio will start playing as soon as it is ready.
	
	
		
	


	
		If present, controls will be displayed, such as a play button.
	
	
		
	


	
		If present, the audio will start over again, every time it is finished.
	
	
		
	


	
		Specifies if the audio should be loaded when the page loads, or not.
		
		Ignored if autoplay is present.
	
	
		
		
		
	


	
		Defines the URL of the audio to play.
	
	

